get_samples_by_gse

Source: R/queries.R
get_samples_by_gse.Rd

get_samples_by_gse

get_samples_by_gse(
  compendium = "vespucci",
  experiment_ExperimentAccessId = "GSE54347"
)

Arguments

compendium

a character - the selected compendium
experiment_ExperimentAccessId

a character - GSE (GEO Series (experiment) access id)

Value

a data.frame with three columns id, sampleName, description

Examples

get_samples_by_gse()
